<p style="margin-top: 1cm; font-size: 300%;"><strong>Magnitude Negative: About</strong></p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/oQeOnuk.png">
<p style="margin-top: 0.4cm; font-size: 200%;">Translator:  <a href="/credits/people/barnabism"><u>Barnabism and Bri</u></a></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.4cm; font-size: 180%;"><strong>Tadashi Aizawa (Author)</strong></p>
<p class="para">Born in 1976, and resides in Tokyo. In 2002, Aizawa made his writing debut after winning a gold medal at the “Resident Evil Novel Awards Ceremony”. He majored in Latin-American Literature in University, and his hobbies are playing and collecting percussion instruments.</p>
<p class="para">Nowadays, in the midst of his on-and-off career of novel-writing, he is also active(?) as an editor and designer. His works are written and created using QuarkXPress.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.4cm; font-size: 180%;"><strong>TASA (Illustrator)</strong></p>
<p class="para">Born in Hiroshima, 1976. After leaving a gaming company, he now works as a freelance illustrator. In addition to doing character designs for games and illustrations for magazines, he is also in charge of the overall artwork for the “Ragnarok” series (Sneaker Publishing). <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20081028103239/http:/www.f8.dion.ne.jp/~hikuta/gallerytop.htm">http://www.f8.dion.ne.jp/~hikuta/gallerytop.html</a></p>
